15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
17 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 2803.3 of Title 12, unless there
18 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
19 A statement that purports to narrate, describe, report, or
20 explain an incident or incidents of domestic abuse as defined in
21 Section 60.1 of Title 22 of the Oklahoma Statutes:
22 1. Made by the victim of domestic abuse to a law enforcement
23 officer within one (1) week of the incident;
